text:
Dubai South signs a strategic Memorandum of Understanding with Emirates NBD to support the financial growth of SMEs within Dubai South. As part of the MoU, Emirates NBD will support companies through streamlined processes for opening corporate bank accounts, alongside tailored banking solutions designed to meet evolving business needs 
